Peacock Lenders Hire KPMG to Review Business, Sunday Times Says

-- B y   E d u a r d   G i s m a t u l l i n
-- 
2011-09-18T09:28:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-18/peacock-lenders-hire-kpmg-to-review-business-sunday-times-says.html
Peacock Group Plc’s lenders,
including  Lloyds Banking Group Plc (LLOY) , have hired KPMG to review
the U.K. clothing retailer’s business, the Sunday Times
 reported , without saying where it got the information.  KPMG will prepare an independent report on Peacock’s
finances amid concerns that the store-chain may breach its
banking covenants, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduard Gismatullin in London at 
 egismatullin@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Kennedy at   wkennedy3@bloomberg.net  